text.en_US:
\C[#CC00CC]Purp\C[]
\C[#E5F8F4]Wht\C[]
\C[#EB6950]Orange\C[]
\C[#A80000]Red\C[]
\C[#6CE9E1]SkyBlue\C[]
\C[#9A3C0E]Brown\C[]
\C[#F7FFBA]Yellow\C[]
Nevermind
Yes
No
Rest until evening?
Sleep until morning?
I can't rest now. There is something I should be doing.

\C[#FBFF99]RedBook\C[]

A red book

\C[#FBFF99]Blue book\C[]
A blue book in a strange language

\C[#FBFF99]Phone\C[]

For checking my stats, social media, quests, calls,
text messages, and gallery.

\C[#FBFF99]Crowbar\C[]

Can pry open tough, unlocked seals

\C[#FBFF99]Multitool\C[]

A useful tool with multiple uses.

\C[#FBFF99]Battery\C[]

Powers an electronic device. Single use.

\C[#FBFF99]Knife\C[]

Sharpy sharp

\C[#FBFF99]Sake\C[]

An asian drink meant to ease anxiety
and melt hearts

\C[#FBFF99]Wine\C[]

Red wine

\C[#FBFF99]Moonshine\C[]

Distilled liquor

\C[#FBFF99]USB Flash Drive\C[]

Used for storing data and delivering elsewhere.

\C[#FBFF99]Fishing Pole\C[]

I could probably catch some fish with this if I 
use it in the right spot.

\C[#FBFF99]Rock\C[]

Nothing special here. Just a rock.
Could throw it at certain things to knock them
over, or just for amusement.

\C[#FBFF99]Red Potion?\C[]

A bottle of some red liquid. No label.
What could this be?

\C[#FBFF99]Map\C[]

What is this, 1995? Just use a GPS for cryin'
out loud.

\C[#FBFF99]Letter\C[]

A postmarked letter

\C[#FBFF99]Screwdriver\C[]

Unscrews things

\C[#FBFF99]Flashlight\C[]

Emits light in dark places.

\C[#FBFF99]Radio\C[]

Communicate with other people that have radios.

\C[#FBFF99]PDA\C[]

A personal digital assistant belonging to....
Somebody? Wonder what's in it.

\C[#FBFF99]Blue Vase\C[]

Would probably break if I dropped this.

\C[#FBFF99]Seashell\C[]

Just a shell. Nothing special..
(i think)

\C[#FBFF99]Firebird South\C[]

Someone said this feather can raise the dead

\C[#FBFF99]Moonrock\C[]

Strange rock that resembles the Moon. Emits a light glow.

\C[#FBFF99]Green Plant\C[]

A common herb used for common reasons.

\C[#FBFF99]Red Leaf\C[]

An uncommon plant is often used in crafting

\C[#FBFF99]Yellow Plant\C[]

A rare herb that has no uses alone, but when combined
produces various results.

\C[#FBFF99]Eggplant\C[]

Why would someone text me saying they want this? So weird.

\C[#FBFF99]Poison\C[]

Probably shouldnt drink this

\C[#FBFF99]Ink Bottle\C[]

A bottle of ink

\C[#FBFF99]ID Card\C[]

A fake ID Card that allows me to make
certain purchases.

\C[#FBFF99]ID-10T\C[]

Another form of ID

\C[#FBFF99]Bronze Key\C[]

A simple key. Unlocks things.

\C[#FBFF99]Silver Key\C[]

A large key. Opens treasure chests.

\C[#FBFF99]Gold Key\C[]

Unlocks rare treasures.

\C[#CC00CC]Nancy\C[]
\C[#E5F8F4]Amelia\C[]
\C[#EB6950]Myra\C[]
\C[#A80000]Sophia\C[]
\C[#6CE9E1]Pearl\C[]
\C[#9A3C0E]Melda\C[]
\C[#9794C5]Maxine\C[]

I can't read this. It's in a weird language.
Maybe someone can help me with it?
Not without something to use this on.
